  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Parse Outcomes / Fallback Usage**: 看导入链路在哪类来源和 parser 上失败，是否频繁退化到 fallback。\n- **Stage Latency P95**: `fetch / parse / clean / quality_score / llm_fallback / parse_commit / chunk / embed / persist / end_to_end` 的 P95 耗时。\n- **Markdown Quality Avg**: Markdown 总质量分均值，用于观察结构完整度和噪声变化。\n- **Structure Score Avg**: 标题层级、列表、表格、图片、链接五类结构得分均值。\n- **Doc Type Outcomes / Quality**: 把 PDF、扫描件、Word、HTML、Markdown 等解析质量拆开看。\n- **Content Ready Latency / Chunk Count P95**: 体现用户何时能看到正文，以及结构切分规模是否异常。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时解析结果。失败时结合 parser 和 error_tag 看异常聚集在哪类文档。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:ingest_parse_total:increase1h",
          "legendFormat": "{{input_type}} / {{status}} / {{parser}} / {{error_tag}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Parse Outcomes (Last 1h)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "最近 1 小时在正文抓取阶段使用的 fallback 次数。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:ingest_fallback_total:increase1h",
          "legendFormat": "{{fallback_type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Fallback Usage (Last 1h)",
      "type": "barchart"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "导入各阶段的 P95 耗时，优先看 success 曲线。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 0,
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "notebooklm:ingest_stage_duration_ms:p95_rate5m{status=~\"success|queued|skipped\"}",
          "legendFormat": "{{stage}} / {{input_type}} / {{status}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Stage Latency P95",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Markdown 质量分均值，适合观察结构完整度和噪声变化趋势。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 2,
          "max": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "none"
